            "children": [
              {
                "text": "Show the character's return to their situation in the ordinary world. Demonstrate whether the situation is changed and made better as a result of their actions, made worse, or if the situation remains unchanged. However, be sure to show the resolution of the problem, whether or not the character was successful."
